https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=42541	24677
<a href="http://www.bootingman.org">闻其详</a> 写道 "
新年伊始，开发者<a href="http://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89">黄志伟</a>宣布&nbsp;<span class="wp_keywordlink_affiliate" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><span style="-webkit-transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-duration: 0.2s; -webkit-transition-timing-function: ease-out; transition-timing-function: ease-out; -webkit-transition-delay: initial; transition-delay: initial; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Android-x86</span></span>&nbsp;4.4 R2 发布，4.4-r2 版本基于&nbsp;<span class="wp_keywordlink_affiliate" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><span style="-webkit-transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-duration: 0.2s; -webkit-transition-timing-function: ease-out; transition-timing-function: ease-out; -webkit-transition-delay: initial; transition-delay: initial; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Android</span></span>&nbsp;4.4.4_r2 (KitKat-MR2.2)并 修复了 x86 相关的一些问题，特别是<span id="1_nwp" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">平板</span>和上网本，与 R1 版本比较，该版本增加如下新特性：<i>
<ul style="margin: 0px 0px 20px 45px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: square outside none; background: transparent;">
<li style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">内核升级到 3.18 ，支持更多新的硬件，如 Intel&nbsp;<span class="wp_keywordlink_affiliate" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><span style="-webkit-transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-duration: 0.2s; -webkit-transition-timing-function: ease-out; transition-timing-function: ease-out; -webkit-transition-delay: initial; transition-delay: initial; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Bay Trail</span></span>&nbsp;platform</li>
<li style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">支持从UEFI 启动</li>
<li style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">改进了挂起和恢复的功能</li>
<li style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">升级很多软件包</li>
<li style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">大量的 bug 修复</li></ul>
</i>
